data.description: Beautiful spacious two story home, three bedrooms all upstairs to include an extra super spacious room that can be used as a playroom, bedroom, movie room, two and half baths, living room, den, breakfast area, kitchen with loads of cabinet space and pantry, kitchen appliances included, Refrigerated air, double garage, front yard landscaped, sprinkler system, two covered patios in big backyard with big shade trees.
